---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Our privacy policy will help you understand what information is collected and how it is used."
  title="Privacy policy Â· Stone"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 sm:py-20 lg:px-8">
    <div class="sm:pb:20 flex flex-col gap-4 pb-16 text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-medium tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-base">Last update: Sept 10, 2023</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <p class="mb-4">
        At JS Web Solutions, we take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy
        outlines how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you interact with our 
        website or services. By accessing or using our website and services, you consent to the practices 
        described in this policy. 
      </p>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl border-b">Information We Collect</h2>
      <ol class="list-inside space-y-4 list-decimal">
        <li>
          <strong>Personal Information:</strong> When you use our services or contact us, we may collect personal information 
          such as your name, email address, phone number, and any other information you provide to us.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Usage Information:</strong> We may collect non-personal information about your interactions with our website and services, 
          including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and other usage data.
        </li>
      </ol>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl border-b">How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">We may use your personal information for various purposes:</p>
      <ul class="list-inside list-disc list space-y-4">
        <li>To provide, maintain, and improve our website and services.</li>
        <li>To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and provide customer support.</li>
        <li>To send you updates, promotional materials, and other information about our services.</li>
        <li>To monitor and analyze usage patterns and trends to enhance our website and services.</li>
        <li>To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights and interests.</li>
      </ul>
      <h2 class="mb-6 mt-12 text-xl font-medium sm:text-2xl">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at
        <a href="mailto:jas.sprinkle@gmail.com">jas.sprinkle@gmail.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
